LIMPOPO – The N1 North is closed near Ingwe following a bus accident. Transport media liaison officer Mike Maringa said the bus allegedly overturned after the driver lost control. “Four people have been declared dead so far and emergency personnel are on the ground trying to rescue trapped passengers,” he said. As a result, Maringa said the N1 North will be closed for several hours and motorists driving between Louis Trichardt and Musina are advised to use the Witvlag Road. 